{"tid":2377540,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"海港Sir公司賣無註冊藥冒牌貨 涉詐騙被搜辦公室 呻「人善被人欺」","createTime":"2021-01-23T16:37:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-24T14:29:15.000Z","uid":5195,"like":72,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"d8bc0524169ea875b9dd188947ff286511aeeca7","tid":2377540,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T16:37:28.000Z","msg":"《蘋果》早前揭發，人稱「海港Sir」的「警隊KOL」警司陳凱港有份出資的「王子商城」疑違法賣無註冊藥膏，有關藥膏雖已下架，但無阻陳續為「王子商城」和其個人品牌「小王子」的產品宣傳。《蘋果》獲悉，「王子商城」最近被指涉及詐騙遭警方調查，其辦公室同遭搜查，陳凱港被警方邀請落口供。《蘋果》記者上周四（21日）下午到「王子商城」地址查詢，職員聲稱「唔知」警察有否登門，又「訓示」記者：「我哋無新聞價值㗎，你唔好再嚟喇！」警方稱不評論個別個案，並稱非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，定必嚴正處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210124/NPZTNUVY35FF3GAND4KUGUFQWQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210124%2FNPZTNUVY35FF3GAND4KUGUFQWQ%2F&d=m1YmCj491ZwsIKcmlD2TapmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=b21af72b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210124%2FNPZTNUVY35FF3GAND4KUGUFQWQ%2F&h=09734db5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210124/NPZTNUVY35FF3GAND4KUGUFQWQ/</a>"},{"pid":"df72e6a9f465bb8ec8be7474dababb48d2752298","tid":2377540,"uid":14422,"like":3,"dislike":14,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T16:39:51.000Z","msg":"肥佬黎都係衰串謀詐騙喎"},{"pid":"a061f81bd4189ce6e5338ec0d6d020536b81fd42","tid":2377540,"uid":253954,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T16:42:30.000Z","msg":"香港警察，知法犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4485f6033e10727dcf4134a31b318fa15f8b36ff","tid":2377540,"uid":187192,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T16:42:34.000Z","msg":"李梓敬定唔知好似有建制派kol既網站有幫手賣呢隻警犬既野, 唔知佢哋使唔使俾人搜查辦公室<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab915747fd710c818327beeaa7261fb3ba5f0948","tid":2377540,"uid":230104,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-